that is JavaScript or C++ or

00:38:33.590 --> 00:38:35.270
ActionScript or Dart.

00:38:35.270 --> 00:38:36.930
The really interesting thing
is, when you talk about

00:38:36.930 --> 00:38:39.490
investment over time as a
developer, as a programmer you

00:38:39.490 --> 00:38:41.000
care about how you're building
your libraries.

00:38:41.000 --> 00:38:43.180
