Haxe, you're kind of

00:38:43.180 --> 00:38:46.290
future-proofing how you're
moving forward, because at

00:38:46.290 --> 00:38:48.910
bare minimum you could do a
source-to-source translation

00:38:48.910 --> 00:38:51.020
